<?php
return ['messages'=>['<p><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;">EJI</span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;">, the renowned fine jewellery manufacturer based in Hong Kong, is thrilled to launch its enchanting “Afternoon Tea” collection, exclusively for CIIE 2024. Celebrating our 7th consecutive year of participation at CIIE, this vibrant and delightful harmony of sweet flavours perfectly complements our “Fine Jewellery, Reimaged” collection. </span></p>'=>'<p><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;">香港高級珠寶製造商</span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;">EJI 推出專為2024年中國國際進博會打造的「下午茶」系列，慶祝品牌連續第七年參展。此系列以甜美意蘊為靈感，與「Fine Jewellery, Reimaged」系列相輔相成，展現盎然活力。  </span></p>','<p><span class="trx_addons_accent">5-10 Nov (Tue-Sun) 0800 - 1800</span></p>'=>'<p><span class="trx_addons_accent">2024年11月5日～10日（二～日）8:00am – 6:00pm</span></p>','<p><span class="trx_addons_dark">Booth A2-04, Hall 6.2, National Exhibition and Convention Center (Shanghai),</span><span style="color: var(--theme-color-text_dark); font-size: 16px; background-color: var(--theme-color-bg_color); letter-spacing: 0px;"> 333 Songze Avenue, Shanghai, China</span></p>'=>'<p><span class="trx_addons_dark">國家會展中心（上海）6.2 館 A2-04</span> 展位<br><span style="color: var(--theme-color-text_dark); font-size: 16px; background-color: var(--theme-color-bg_color); letter-spacing: 0px;">中國上海市崧澤大道 333 號</span></p>','<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;">As an innovative and creative fine jeweller, the “Afternoon Tea” collection features a variety of artfully presented miniature sweet jewellery creations, designed to enchant your senses. This stunning array of desserts, delicately crafted in 18K gold and the finest ingredients, includes intricately designed flower layer cakes, macarons, and doughnuts and more, all beautifully displayed on a three-tier cake stand. Complemented by two refreshing glasses of champagne, it adds a touch of celebration and luxurious ensemble. </span></p>'=>'<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;">作為兼具創新與藝術的珠寶匠師，EJI以「下午茶」系列呈獻精巧的甜點造型珠寶。作品採用18K金與頂級材質精心打造，涵蓋花式層糕、馬卡龍、甜甜圈等造型，細緻精美，盛放於三層展示架上，令人讚歎。搭配兩杯清爽香檳，更添慶典與奢華氣息。   </span></p>','<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;">Not to be missed is the versatility of these jewellery creations. They are not just for display; they can be transformed into wearable jewellery, perfect for any occasions; and adding a touch of elegance to whatever attire. The “Afternoon Tea” collection is an experience that celebrates the art of indulgence. For lovers of sweet treats, these wonderful delicacies satisfy cravings with the ultimate festive touch, celebrating life’s finest moments.</span></p>'=>'<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;">此系列珠寶不僅供欣賞，更可化為可佩戴的飾品，適合各種場合，為服飾增添一抹優雅。甜點愛好者可在此滿足味蕾，感受節慶的極致魅力，慶祝美好時刻。   </span></p>','<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;">The “Fine Jewellery, Reimaged” collection is renowned for redefining the art of jewellery with cutting-edge design, seamlessly blending into everyday life with infinite creativity, meticulous craftsmanship and luxurious elegance. We promise our new collection redefines fine jewellery with an elegant yet playful nod to the afternoon tea tradition, bringing an exceptional moment of luxury and whimsy to your personal jewellery box.</span></p><p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;">Our passion for excellence and bespoke jewellery service inspires us to craft one-of-a-kind fine jewellery just for you. We cordially invite you to indulge in the elegance of our “Afternoon Tea” collection and treat yourself to these vibrant jewellery creations now at CIIE in Shanghai. We welcome you to explore a world of possibilities and imagination – embracing new moments with us. And so, our journey of indulgence continues…</span></p>'=>'<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;">「Fine Jewellery, Reimaged」系列以突破性設計重新定義珠寶藝術，融合無限創意、精湛工藝與奢華優雅，無縫融入日常生活。新系列以輕鬆而優雅的方式致敬下午茶傳統，為您的珠寶收藏增添奢華與奇趣。 </span></p><p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;">誠摯邀請您於上海進博會體驗「下午茶」系列的優雅，沉浸於這些充滿活力的珠寶創作。歡迎您探索無限可能與想像，與我們共創嶄新時刻，延續藝術之旅。   </span></p>','<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;">Translating the lustrous sophistication of jewellery creation into the most alluring delicacies, the “Afternoon Tea” collection offers a unique and exquisite twist on the traditional afternoon tea experience. Highlights include unparalleled craftsmanship and unique designs, with intricate details showcasing the highest level of artistry and sophistication. Each bite is a testament to our deep passion for jewellery design and our unwavering pursuit of excellence. </span></p>'=>'<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;">「下午茶」系列將珠寶創作的璀璨魅力融入誘人珍饈，為傳統下午茶體驗注入獨特風采。其特色在於無與倫比的工藝與獨創設計。每件作品，都體現我們對珠寶設計的深厚熱情與對卓越的不懈追求。   </span></p>','<p><strong><big>Follow us</big></strong></p>'=>'<p><strong><big>關注我們</big></strong></p>','<p>Visit <a href="https://www.ciie.org/zbh/en/"><em><strong>ciie.org/zbh/en/ </strong></em></a>for more about the show’s events.</p>'=>'<p>訪問 <a href="https://www.ciie.org/zbh/en/"><em><strong>ciie.org/zbh/en/ </strong></em></a>瞭解有關展會活動的更多資訊。</p>','A Feast for the Eyes and Palate'=>'視覺與品味的盛宴','Book Your Appointment'=>'與我們的團隊聯繫','DISCOVER THE COLLECTION'=>'探索系列','Location'=>'地點','Masterpieces of Craftsmanship'=>'匠心傑作','Show Hours'=>'展會日期','The Art of Versatility'=>'多變的藝術','editor-text-editor-199946b'=>'<p><strong><big>關注我們</big></strong></p>','editor-text-editor-4686db8'=>'<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;">「Fine Jewellery, Reimaged」系列以突破性設計重新定義珠寶藝術，融合無限創意、精湛工藝與奢華優雅，無縫融入日常生活。新系列以輕鬆而優雅的方式致敬下午茶傳統，為您的珠寶收藏增添奢華與奇趣。 </span></p><p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;">誠摯邀請您於上海進博會體驗「下午茶」系列的優雅，沉浸於這些充滿活力的珠寶創作。歡迎您探索無限可能與想像，與我們共創嶄新時刻，延續藝術之旅。   </span></p>','editor-text-editor-7bd2f7f'=>'<p>訪問 <a href="https://www.ciie.org/zbh/en/"><em><strong>ciie.org/zbh/en/ </strong></em></a>瞭解有關展會活動的更多資訊。</p>','editor-text-editor-8e06f71'=>'<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;">「下午茶」系列將珠寶創作的璀璨魅力融入誘人珍饈，為傳統下午茶體驗注入獨特風采。其特色在於無與倫比的工藝與獨創設計。每件作品，都體現我們對珠寶設計的深厚熱情與對卓越的不懈追求。   </span></p>','editor-text-editor-a251fdd'=>'<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;">此系列珠寶不僅供欣賞，更可化為可佩戴的飾品，適合各種場合，為服飾增添一抹優雅。甜點愛好者可在此滿足味蕾，感受節慶的極致魅力，慶祝美好時刻。   </span></p>','editor-text-editor-b81cfc8'=>'<p><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;">香港高級珠寶製造商</span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;">EJI 推出專為2024年中國國際進博會打造的「下午茶」系列，慶祝品牌連續第七年參展。此系列以甜美意蘊為靈感，與「Fine Jewellery, Reimaged」系列相輔相成，展現盎然活力。  </span></p>','editor-text-editor-ed5b90a'=>'<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;">作為兼具創新與藝術的珠寶匠師，EJI以「下午茶」系列呈獻精巧的甜點造型珠寶。作品採用18K金與頂級材質精心打造，涵蓋花式層糕、馬卡龍、甜甜圈等造型，細緻精美，盛放於三層展示架上，令人讚歎。搭配兩杯清爽香檳，更添慶典與奢華氣息。   </span></p>','https://eji.com.hk/afternoon-tea/'=>'https://eji.com.hk/zh-hant/%e4%b8%8b%e5%8d%88%e8%8c%b6/','mailto:sales@eji.com.hk'=>'mailto:sales@eji.com.hk','text-button-2363fb3'=>'探索系列','text-button-d03948d'=>'與我們的團隊聯繫','title-heading-46527e5'=>'「Fine Jewellery, Reimaged」高級珠寶 風格重塑','title-heading-5d27b11'=>'多變的藝術','title-heading-b37fb63'=>'匠心傑作','title-heading-d5564d2'=>'視覺與品味的盛宴','toggle-tab_content-5884f4d-1424e35'=>'<p><span class="trx_addons_accent">2024年11月5日～10日（二～日）8:00am – 6:00pm</span></p>','toggle-tab_content-5884f4d-a702809'=>'<p><span class="trx_addons_dark">國家會展中心（上海）6.2 館 A2-04</span> 展位<br><span style="color: var(--theme-color-text_dark); font-size: 16px; background-color: var(--theme-color-bg_color); letter-spacing: 0px;">中國上海市崧澤大道 333 號</span></p>','toggle-tab_title-5884f4d-1424e35'=>'展會日期','toggle-tab_title-5884f4d-a702809'=>'地點','url-button-2363fb3'=>'https://eji.com.h